      "author": "shuxueshuxue",
      "description": "  All Issues Addressed\r\n\r\n  1. Empty URLs in manifest.json\r\n  - Removed empty \"authorUrl\": \"\", and \"helpUrl\": \"\", fields from manifest.json\r\n\r\n  2. No unnecessary console logging\r\n  - Added process.env.NODE_ENV === 'development' checks around all console.log statements\r\n\r\n  3. Command should be conditional\r\n  - Changed from callback to checkCallback that only enables when active file exists\r\n\r\n  4. Manual frontmatter removal\r\n  - Replaced all regex-based frontmatter removal with getFrontMatterInfo\r\n\r\n  5. Command ID includes plugin prefix\r\n  - Fixed: 'open-packup4ai-notes' → 'collect-notes'\r\n\r\n  6. Command name now makes sense\r\n  -  'Open packup4AI Notes' → 'Collect notes for AI context'\r\n\r\n  7. UI text not in sentence case\r\n  - Updated all UI elements to sentence case:\r\n    - \"Collection Settings\" → \"Collection settings\"\r\n    - \"Include Backlinks\" → \"Include backlinks\"\r\n    - \"Output Filename\" → \"Output filename\"\r\n    - \"Collect & Copy to Clipboard\" → \"Collect & copy to clipboard\"\r\n    - And all other instances\r\n\r\n  8. Path normalization missing\r\n  - Fixed: Added normalizePath calls for all user input paths\r\n\r\n  9. Settings tab heading structure\r\n  - Removed top-level `<h2>` heading from settings tab per guidelines\r\n\r\n  10. D3 CDN dependency\r\n  - local D3 inclusion",
